Chat persistence + rich prompts + system status widget

- useChatHistory hook: localStorage + Supabase chat_messages sync
- Agent chat and Command center now persist messages to Supabase
- Clear chat button (Trash2) on agent pages and command center
- Enriched all 8 agent system prompts with real project context
  (MyReply metrics, Edison details, target audiences, frameworks)
- System status widget on HQ: shows OpenRouter/Supabase/PWA status
- Command center refactored to use unified ChatMsg type
- Mobile improvements: hidden mic button on small screens, wider bubbles
